Package queues

Class Jukebox

java.lang.Object
queues.Jukebox
public class Jukebox
extends java.lang.Object
Manages three objects of type Queue where a Queue object represents a playlist. Possible valid playlists are "favorites", "lounge" and "road trip", called favoritesPL, loungePL and roadTripPL respectively.
